practitionersModule.title: Join the community of professional and independent practitioners in the world of holistic health!
practitionersModule.mission: Our mission is to gather all qualified practitioners within holistic health, support them in their entrepreneurship, and make their services easily understandable and searchable for everyone in need - whether it's treatments, education, experiences, or just a curious exploration of life!
practitionersModule.belief: We are convinced that together with you as a health entrepreneur, we will quickly increase the general acceptance of alternative and complementary methods - thereby contributing to the health revolution that has already begun!
practitionersModule.featurePracticeTitle: One digital storefront and all essential tools

featurePracticeSteps.step1: Access our intuitive digital publishing tool, where you effortlessly showcase your entire range of services in a search-optimized, well-designed, and structured manner – all to maximize your visibility and quickly attract new customers.
featurePracticeSteps.step2: Optimize your schedule and customer bookings in our booking system where customer records, journal notes, and payment solutions are included. Alternatively, choose to continue using your existing booking system with just a few simple clicks.
featurePracticeSteps.step3: Automatically follow up on the customer experience - fully integrated with Google My Business - and increase your digital visibility. All while positioning yourself better - both within Holistikah and on the web at large!

practitionersModule.platformTitle: One system for all your needs
practitionersModule.platformDescriptions: Market your company and create detailed descriptions of all your services and events using our user-friendly tool. All integrated with our flexible booking system or, if you prefer, your existing booking system.

item1.title: Optimize your schedule
item1.descriptions: Eliminate inefficiency and save time with our intuitive tool for optimized time management. Manage desired work hours, bookings, and payments in a system where customer records, journal notes, and automatic reminders are included as standard features.

item2.title: All-in-One Management
item2.descriptions: Manage your diverse service offering in one solution! With our integrated system, you receive powerful support whether you offer treatments, group events, classes, coaching, training, or workshops.

item3.title: Boost Google Rankings
item3.descriptions: To be visible on the internet is crucial to reach your target audience. Our proven solution enhances your ranking on search engines, leading to increased exposure and more business opportunities.

item4.title: Effortless online presence
item4.descriptions: To create and maintain websites is time-consuming and expensive. With HOLISTIKAH, you avoid unnecessary administration while enjoying a premium designed digital presentation of your offering.

practitionersModule.onlinePaymentDescriptions: Simplify your customers' payments with our integrated payment solution! Minimize the risk of 'no-shows' and streamline cash management through regular payouts directly to your bank account.

packagePlan.alwaysIncludedStep4: Seamless integration to external booking system

holipreneurScaling.title: Grow your business with HOLIPRENEUR -
holipreneurScaling.subTitle: the catalyst that strengthens your offering and takes your company to new heights!
holipreneurScaling.description1: Are you a practitioner in need of a community - with support and education to bolster your practice and reach more clients? In the entrepreneur community of Holipreneur, we offer events, courses, programs, and masterclasses in entrepreneurship and marketing, among others.
holipreneurScaling.description2: Holipreneur is a subscription and add-on service. As a practitioner with HOLISTIKAH, you always receive reduced prices on both subscription fees and individual courses and programs.
holipreneurScaling.description3: With Holipreneur's assistance, you'll develop new strategies, enhance your leadership skills, refine your marketing, and make selling your services natural and straightforward - all tailored specifically for the holistic health industry.
holipreneurScaling.description4: Join us today and let's shape the future of your business together. With Holipreneur by your side, you'll gain the tools, guidance, and support needed to navigate industry challenges and achieve sustainable growth.
holipreneurScaling.description5: We believe in the power of action – because action always leads to results and change!
holipreneurScaling.step2: Niched and easy to implement on-line courses
holipreneurScaling.step3: Multilevel mastermind groups and programs for growing and collaboration
holipreneurScaling.step4: In depth 1-1 signature programs for real fast scaling and growth

practitionersModule.seoTitle: Velora  | Stylish Clothing for Every Occasion
practitionersModule.seoDescription: Discover Velora’s curated collection of trendy clothing designed for comfort, style, and confidence. Shop fashion-forward outfits, everyday essentials, and timeless pieces to elevate your wardrobe.

aboutUsModule.metaDataDescription: Learn how Velora crafts stylish, comfortable, and sustainable clothing you’ll love.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsDescription: Velora is a modern clothing brand focused on quality fabrics, thoughtful design, and fair pricing.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsPara1: Welcome to Velora — your destination for effortless fashion. We curate everyday essentials and trend-forward pieces that fit beautifully and last beyond the season.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsPara2: Premium materials, precise fits, and transparent pricing. We obsess over details so you don’t have to.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsSubPara2: From work-ready staples to weekend layers, our collections are designed for real life and all its moments.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsPara3: We prioritize responsible sourcing, low-impact dyes, and durable construction to extend each garment’s life.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsSubPara3: Better choices today mean wardrobes that last longer and leave a lighter footprint.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsPara4: Every piece is cut for comfort and crafted to flatter — so you can feel as good as you look.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsSubPara4: Discover quality denim, breathable cottons, and soft knits you’ll reach for again and again.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsPara5: Velora is built with you. We listen, iterate, and design with feedback from our community.
aboutUsModule.aboutUsPara6: We’re here to make great style simple — with drops you’ll love and service that delights.
aboutUsModule.coFounder1Description: With a love for craftsmanship and customer experience, we started Velora to make great style accessible without compromise.
aboutUsModule.coFounder2Description: We design with intention — creating pieces that mix seamlessly and last longer.
aboutUsModule.coFounder3Description: Our sourcing partners share our standards for quality, ethics, and sustainability.
aboutUsModule.coFounder4Description: From warehouse to wardrobe, we optimize every step to deliver value you can feel.
aboutUsModule.mobileOurTeamPara: A small team with a big love for timeless style.
aboutUsModule.seoDescription: Discover Velora’s story: thoughtful design, premium fabrics, and sustainable choices.

symptomsModule.title: Symptoms
symptomsModule.descriptions: When searching by symptom, we provide suggestions for various treatment methods that typically address the underlying causes of the searched symptoms. It's important to note that each healing process is unique to every individual, and therefore, results may vary from person to person. In other words, there are never any guarantees that the recommended methods will help you specifically.
symptomsModule.seoTitle: HOLISTIKAH | Holistic health - Guide by symptom
symptomsModule.seoDescription: Discover effective holistic health treatments tailored to your symptoms. Explore a diverse range of holistic therapies to address your unique well-being needs. Find natural solutions and practitioners dedicated to your holistic healing journey.

holipediaModule.title: Holipedia
holipediaModule.desktopDescriptionsPara1: In The Holipedia, you can read about various treatment methods and activities that promote holistic health and increased well-being.
holipediaModule.desktopDescriptionsPara2: It is important to note that the symptoms listed under different treatment methods are the symptoms that each respective method typically addresses to resolve underlying causes of imbalance and illness. However, each healing process is unique to each individual, and results therefore vary from person to person. In other words, there are never any guarantees that the recommended methods will help you specifically.The desire to get well and the willingness to make the changes that promote improved health and increased well-being are always the first steps to healing and positive development.
